<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Form_Element_File override getErrors(), hasErrors() and getMessages() to transfer the method to the adapter.
However, the following functions are not overridden.</p>

<pre><code>    addError()
    addErrors()
    addErrorMessage()
    addErrorMessages()
    setErrors()
    setErrorMessages()
    clearErrorMessages()
</code></pre>

<p>So for example "$errors = $form-&gt;getErrors();" after "$form-&gt;addError($msg);" does not work as expected but returns nothing.</p>

<p>Please make them work as expected,
or just override those functions to throw the exception (if you do not have much time)</p>

